preambule.al:
Whereas the Kingdom of Sweden wishes to assist the
Kingdom of the Netherlands, in respect of Aruba, in diversifying its
economy;

li.al:
in
Aruba: the profit tax (de winstbelasting) (hereinafter referred to as
“Aruban tax”);

the term
“company” means any body corporate or any entity that is
treated as a body corporate for tax purposes;

industrial
and manufacturing activities, including assembly
activities;

op
Aruba: de winstbelasting (hierna te noemen „Arubaanse
belasting”);

industriële
en productieactiviteiten, met inbegrip van
assemblagewerkzaamheden;

een
